PrecisAppointment of the following persons as directors of the board of directors of the Canada Pension Plan Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of two years. (JACK LEVI, of Vancouver, British Columbia; SUSAN CARNELL, of Toronto, Ontario; RICHARD McALONEY, of Lower Sackville, Nova Scotia; PIERRE MICHAUD, of Montreal, Quebec; HELEN MEYER, of Erin, Ontario; and MARY ARNOLD, of Edmonton, Alberta)
